'''Tarka''' neɣ '''Taserka''' d [[aṭṭan]] [[aṭṭan amanṭaṭ|amanṭaṭ]] xeddment-id [[Timadanin|tmadanin]] [[Yersinia pestis|tiyersinin]] yettwasemma s yisem n umusnaw n tbiktirin Afrensaw [[Alexandre Yersin]]. Alammi d [[yunyu]] [[2007]] tarka tella d yiwet gar n 3 n [[Tasakrart|tsakrarin]] ɣef acu yessefk ad yettulɣet fell-as ar [[tuddsa tamadlant n tdawsa]] (sin n waṭṭanen n iden gan d [[taburdit]] yakk d [[tawla tawraɣt]]).<ref>[http://www.who.int/ihr/ihr_brief_no_2_en.pdf WHO IHR Brief No. 2. Notification and other reporting requirements under the IHR (2005)] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120130235443/http://www.who.int/ihr/ihr_brief_no_2_en.pdf |date=30 yennayer 2012}}</ref>

S ugani (litkal) ɣef [[azzug|wazzug]] n [[turin]] d twetlin tidawsanin, tarka tezmer ad tenfufed deg [[azwu|wezwu]], s unermis usrid neɣ s wučči n tnegwa yeblulɣen neɣ yummsen s ibiktiren yerna ur wwint ara akken iwata. [[Askan|Isekna]] n tarka d wid yeggunin ɣef tamiwin yudnen g [[tafekka|tfekka]] am [[tarka n timmist]] g [[awles alimfaw|iwelsen ilimfawen]], [[Tarka mturin]] g [[turin]] d ugerjum

